plot: A rival supernatural commando squad, the SDCD, is called in to clean up the mess left behind by their counterparts. What they discover will leave them reeling in disbelief. Could one of their own be responsible for the massacre?
title: "Ga-rei: Zero" Nikushimi no hatsuro
